        "text": "Confederation of Finnish Industries (EK) is the leading business organization in Finland, representing 19 member associations and 15,300 member companies across all business sectors. EK's member companies employ 900,000 employees. EK is a member of BusinessEurope and IOE, and is also active in the OECD and the ILO.",
