        "text": "EK urges the Commission to prioritize the effective enforcement and simplification of existing rules, to conduct robust impact assessments, and to avoid introducing new regulation unless a genuine legislative gap is identified. Any new measures must be proportionate, targeted, and coherent with the broader EU legal framework, including ePrivacy. The needs of SMEs, the media sector, and the importance of legal certainty and competitiveness must be at the forefront of the DFA's development.",
